This directory is used to store third-party service integrations:

Directory structure:

    /
    |- conf/
    |- dialog/
    |- extra/
        |- pureftpd/
            |- README
            |- conf/        # <- files contain pre-defined variables.
            |- dialog/      # <- dialog pages as setup wizard.
            |- functions/   # <- functions used to install, configure, cleanup program.
            |- patches/     # <- patches
            |- pureftpd.sh  # <- Main script
            |- ...
        |- app_name2/ 
        |- app_name3/ 
    |- functions/
    |- iRedMail.sh
    |- patches/
    |- pkgs/
    |- samples/
    |- tools
